text: Apne ko to abhi ek saal aur h, Lekin bs tu hi hai mera food cravings ka partner. "Bhai chickblast jaane ki iccha ho rhi", "Aaj BBQ chale" kabhi in questions ka answer NO nhi mila. Here to our Thesis and possible return to campus.

text:
Bhai kya hi bakchodiyaan ki h tere saath, wo under construction Hall 13, heated arguments about similarities b/w Ronaldo and Kohli, And most funny one "Why some trees have bent branches?". But all these are fun memories framed in our minds. But they won't be the last. 
Bsdk milte rhenge warna maa chod denge.
